    Note over Alice,Network: ═══════════ ALLOCATION → OFFER (Bootstrap State) ═══════════
    Note over Alice,Network: 🤖 AUTOMATIC: Providers observe needs, compute allocations, publish offers<br/>💡 KEY: Allocation (derived) → Offer (commitment via policy)<br/>⏰ TIMING: Happens anytime provider observes needs (continuous, async)
    
    par Parallel Automatic Offering (Providers compute & publish automatically)
        rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
            Note over Carol: 📊 AUTOMATIC COMPUTATION (Derived State)
            Carol->>Carol: Observe: Alice needs 100, Bob needs 90<br/><br/>📐 MUTUAL RECOGNITION (Eligibility):<br/>  MR(Carol,Alice) = min(30%, 30%) = 30%<br/>  MR(Carol,Bob) = min(40%, 40%) = 40%<br/>  Total MR = 70%<br/><br/>📐 RECIPIENT SHARES (Bootstrap - no satisfaction yet):<br/>  Alice's share of Carol = 30% (recognition only)<br/>  Bob's share of Carol = 40% (recognition only)<br/><br/>📐 MUTUAL SATISFACTION (MS = MR × share):<br/>  MS(Carol,Alice) = 30% × 30% = 0.09<br/>  MS(Carol,Bob) = 40% × 40% = 0.16<br/>  Total MS = 0.25<br/><br/>📐 ALLOCATE (MS-based):<br/>  allocation_alice = 150 × (0.09/0.25) = 54<br/>  allocation_bob = 150 × (0.16/0.25) = 96
            Carol->>Carol: 🎯 APPLY POLICY (User-Set, Stable):<br/>commitment_rate = 1.0 (offer 100%)<br/>auto_publish = true<br/><br/>offer_alice = 64.3 × 1.0 = 64.3<br/>offer_bob = 85.7 × 1.0 = 85.7<br/><br/>💡 These offers are COMMITMENTS
            Carol->>Network: 🤖 AUTO-PUBLISH Offers {<br/>  offer_id: "carol_offer_1_alice",<br/>  to: Alice, amount: 54,<br/>  offer_id: "carol_offer_1_bob",<br/>  to: Bob, amount: 96<br/>}
        end
    and
        rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
            Note over Kitchen: 📊 AUTOMATIC COMPUTATION (Derived State)
            Kitchen->>Kitchen: Observe: Alice needs 100, Bob needs 90<br/><br/>📐 MUTUAL RECOGNITION (Eligibility):<br/>  MR(Kitchen,Alice) = min(20%, 20%) = 20%<br/>  MR(Kitchen,Bob) = min(30%, 30%) = 30%<br/>  Total MR = 50%<br/><br/>📐 RECIPIENT SHARES (Bootstrap - no satisfaction yet):<br/>  Alice's share of Kitchen = 20% (recognition only)<br/>  Bob's share of Kitchen = 30% (recognition only)<br/><br/>📐 MUTUAL SATISFACTION (MS = MR × share):<br/>  MS(Kitchen,Alice) = 20% × 20% = 0.04<br/>  MS(Kitchen,Bob) = 30% × 30% = 0.09<br/>  Total MS = 0.13<br/><br/>📐 ALLOCATE (MS-based):<br/>  allocation_alice = 200 × (0.04/0.13) = 61.5<br/>  allocation_bob = 200 × (0.09/0.13) = 138.5
            Kitchen->>Kitchen: 🎯 APPLY POLICY (User-Set, Stable):<br/>commitment_rate = 1.0<br/>auto_publish = true<br/><br/>offer_alice = 61.5 × 1.0 = 61.5<br/>offer_bob = 138.5 × 1.0 = 138.5<br/><br/>✅ Full allocation offered
            Kitchen->>Network: 🤖 AUTO-PUBLISH Offers {<br/>  offer_id: "kitchen_offer_1_alice",<br/>  to: Alice, amount: 61.5,<br/>  offer_id: "kitchen_offer_1_bob",<br/>  to: Bob, amount: 138.5<br/>}
        end
    end

