    Note over Alice,Network: 📐 NEED UPDATE LAW (Automatic):<br/>Need(t+1) = Need(t) - Received(t)<br/><br/>Alice: Need(t) = 100, Received = 48+50 = 98<br/>  → Need(t+1) = 100 - 98 = 2 (nearly satisfied!)<br/><br/>Bob: Need(t) = 90, Received = 45+45 = 90<br/>  → Need(t+1) = 90 - 90 = 0 (fully satisfied!)<br/><br/>💡 Prevents accumulation, ensures convergence

