    Note over Alice,Network: ═══════════ PROVIDER SATISFACTION AGGREGATION (Automatic) ═══════════
    Note over Alice,Network: 🔄 REACTIVE: Providers observe satisfaction, recompute reputation<br/>📐 FORMULA: Weighted average across recipients + EMA smoothing

    par Parallel Reputation Updates (Providers observe automatically)
        rect rgb(230, 230, 250)
            Note over Carol: 📊 AUTOMATIC REPUTATION UPDATE
            Carol->>Carol: Observe satisfaction from network:<br/><br/>From Alice:<br/>  accepted: 50, delivered: 48<br/>  quality: 0.85 (manual rating)<br/>  reliability: 48/50 = 0.96 (automatic)<br/><br/>From Bob:<br/>  accepted: 45, delivered: 45<br/>  quality: 0.60 (manual rating)<br/>  reliability: 45/45 = 1.0 (automatic)<br/><br/>📐 WEIGHTED AVERAGE (across recipients):<br/>  quality_avg = (50×0.85 + 45×0.60) / (50+45)<br/>              = (42.5 + 27) / 95 = 0.731<br/>  reliability_avg = (50×0.96 + 45×1.0) / 95<br/>                  = 0.979<br/><br/>📐 EMA UPDATE (temporal smoothing, α=0.2):<br/>  quality_ema = 0.2×0.731 + 0.8×prev<br/>              = 0.731 (bootstrap, no previous)<br/>  reliability_ema = 0.2×0.979 + 0.8×prev<br/>                  = 0.979<br/><br/>effective_reputation = 0.731 × 0.979 = 0.72
            Note over Carol: 💡 Two-stage aggregation:<br/>1. Weighted by accepted qty<br/>2. EMA smoothing over time
        end
    and
        rect rgb(230, 230, 250)
