ersification<br/>    (1/N strategy preserved throughout)<br/>  ✅ Providers adjust automatically<br/>    (No per-cycle intervention, policy-driven)<br/>  ✅ Periodic recognition updates drive convergence<br/>    (Weekly/monthly adjustments sufficient)<br/>  ✅ Bounded downside, unbounded upside<br/>    (Max loss = need/N, discovery leads to recognition ratchet)<br/>  ✅ Quality signal is clear<br/>    (Kitchen: 0.926 reputation, Carol: 0.72 reputation)<br/>  ✅ Resource utilization efficient<br/>    (All needs met, no waste, capacities utilized)
